name: The Insyderz
description: '''The Insyderz''' were an American [[Christian ska]]-punk [[musical band|band]] from [[Detroit]], [[Michigan]]. They formed in 1996 and disbanded in 2005. The band reformed in 2009, but have not been actively playing shows in the last few years. The Insyderz are one of the "big three" bands which represented the Christian ska scene, alongside the [[Supertones]] and [[Five Iron Frenzy]].
